Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I was locked up in this ice by Atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because you told Atom needless stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian, I'm telling you that no matter how much
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you oppose me, I'm going to carry my wills out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm never going to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom vs. Atlas VII: The Runaway Subway
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-What a speed. -It's 180 kilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-180 kilometers per hour? -What, you didn't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it all right for this to run so fast underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The control center called UATS sends out orders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and computers in these tubes make decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to give out orders of GO or STOP to the subway
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and to control the speed of the subway as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no driver of this subway. Doctor Ochanomizu's team developed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamao, there are many subways in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is only one spot where the subway comes up the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know which station and line that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well... Where, where, where? -That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Point 512 of this X-17. Right before the last station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! You cannot say that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was great. -It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for riding with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last station of X-17. Make sure you have all your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get rid of Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My plans have all been interrupted by Atom all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to think about it, Livian,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you started defying me since Atom showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot take it anymore! I'm going to defeat Atom this time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fight him fairly under the same condition. You don't have any problem, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...So the transportation network of the city of Tokyo is at its peak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by reaching both underground and ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Shibukaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not going to listen to your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher! Atom's not here! -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-He was here just now. -Did he go to toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Why would Atom go to toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-He must be loafing around since he was bored. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! It's the same sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here, Atom! Take your sword! It's a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't want to! -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-You coward. -Coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, I don't want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't want to, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He drew the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work. But the game is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you are out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You bad one. Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, don't fight this hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interrupt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher! Are you all right? -You sure touched me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I stand here, you won't be able to lay a hand on Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oldie, get out. You will get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oldie? How dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in my beautiful forties. Let's have a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing. I'm good at fencing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, there's a disturber. Let's postpone the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Atom? Listen! I'll be back in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to defeat you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In three days? This is not a time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom would be safe in the vault under the Ministry of Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is Atlas so obsessed with Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, Dr. Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We really can't predict what he's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As his teacher, I thought Atom should never fight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,such a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it doesn't feel like we are 60 floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This vault contains confidential documents of the Ministry of Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-The blueprint of Atom is here as well. -My blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't like to hid, but be patient for three days. You have to stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have any problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but... Atlas called me a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be ashamed of that. You shouldn't fight such robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not right, Doctor Ochanomizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't mark you absent for classes, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Read books or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You haven't found Atom yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've installed detectors in all places he might show up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the third day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That Beard and Doctor Ochanomizu must have hidden him for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't Atom coming to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He is hiding deep down the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Deep down the underground? -Oops, I'm not supposed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? You said you wanted to take the subway first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down the underground... Isn't Atom already on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Atom's in a state of emergency now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What state of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I don't know. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take me, too! -Nope. The one who doesn't go to classes can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibukaki, you mean person. Pig, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? So Atom is deep down the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Subway is complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get it wrong. We are going to take that X-17.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it would be at the 10th basement floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The first carriage is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We are at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not kidding. -It just passed by the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening? Why isn't UATS working?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's no manual brake. -It's completely automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how am I supposed to stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My! Tamao, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This cannot be true. This cannot be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do? The train and the machine themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,have no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be good if they had one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly release the first carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency evacuate everyone on X-17.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-It passed by again. -We have to get off this station, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now the third time passing by. What should we do, Kenichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the train ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to crash like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry and change the point! -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-We are crashing! -Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it has joined the W-3 line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is point moving on its own? -It seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency evacuate people in all lines of the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Wouldn't it be too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way but to count on Atom now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The train has entered the S-6 line now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's getting faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 200 kilometers per hour already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why wouldn't it stop? -What's so great about UATS?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -We count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-We are safe now. -Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird. My energy is gone when I get closer to the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you won't be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That subway has the non-energy device on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-energy device?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It absorbs all energy within one meter range.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your 100,000 horse power and UATS energy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For what are you doing all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? I did this to bring you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a coward for hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, how can you think of such scary thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The train has entered the H-15 line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a train coming from the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go backward immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, but the train is running at the speed of 300 kilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We will get caught up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go, then defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are crashing. Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom. -Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The train has evacuated to the C-30 line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the train is now in the K-45 line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. There is a train that hasn't evacuated yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I can stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The train is back to its original X-17 line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,400 kilometers per hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If it keeps speeding up, it will be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that. It's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading to the last station building!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like the station building can be moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. If the evacuation of other trains is over, cut the power off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work! It doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after cutting the power off, the train's not stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the fire and police department. Dispatch them to the station building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But would it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the only way to save people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom! Listen carefully, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only 30 seconds left. We count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, good job. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian, get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, let's go back to Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, Crystal is your castle. I'm with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Africa's robot safari park.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of robot animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But a real elephant got shot by bad hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor baby elephant Pura lost her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, a big elephant robot starts acting violently
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the safari park is turned upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Little Elephant Pura." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "The Little Elephant Pura"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.15,0:24:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
